data.description: Right in the heart of Hamilton, this vintage 4 bedroom home awaits your personal touch to make it shine. Assumable VA loan with no appraisal needed. Upon entry you'll be greeted with a free-standing natural gas stove over country chic flooring. Keep them as-is or sand and stain to uncover the brilliance of the original hardwood floors. Primary bedroom is right off the living room, with second bedroom, one bathroom, and open living/dining space also on the main level. Upstairs you'll find two bedrooms, one large bathroom, and a small nook perfect for cozying up to read a book or enjoy the antics of the squirrels in the mature trees right outside the window. Detached 2 car garage with alley access adds to the large backyard with an oversized deck perfect for entertaining and relaxing. Just minutes from all the amenities of Hamilton, this house is waiting for you to make it a home. Call Dawn Luedecke at 406-546-0445 or your real estate professional.
